#### TASK-UX-001: Create Comprehensive Design Token System
**Priority:** P0 (Foundation)
**Effort:** 2 days
**Related Story:** 8-1-unified-design-tokens

**Description:**
Create CSS custom properties file with complete token system based on competitor analysis.

**Deliverables:**
- [ ] Color tokens (semantic + task colors)
- [ ] Typography scale (5 levels)
- [ ] Spacing scale (1-6)
- [ ] Shadow tokens (elevation)
- [ ] Border radius tokens
- [ ] Animation timing tokens

**Acceptance Criteria:**
- All hardcoded values replaced with tokens
- Dark mode variables complete
- No color literals in component files

